# 🚗 DriveNow - Vehicle Rental Management System

## 📌 Project Description
DriveNow is a MERN stack based vehicle rental system where users can rent vehicles and admins can manage listings.

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Frontend: React (Vite)
- Backend: Node.js, Express
- Database: MongoDB
- Authentication: JWT

---

## 🚀 Features
- User Registration & Login
- JWT Authentication
- Vehicle Listing
- Vehicle Booking System
- Admin Dashboard

---

